.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, trance, jazz, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, handball, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
4. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the fan of jazz is between the fan of soul and the fan of trance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | jazz           | soul | reggae  |
| Sport         | skiing | soccer | handball   | snowboarding |

