.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, funk, r&b, d&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, subway, bike, van
1. the fan of funk is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the fan of techno is between the person driving the airplane and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | funk | techno | r&b      |
| Transport     | bike | airplane    | subway  | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, cricket, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, skateboard, boat
1. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | basketball | baseball | cricket     | cycling   |
| Transport   | skateboard   | scooter     | boat | car |

