.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, police-officer, dancer, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, roller, quad-bike
1. the dancer is between the person driving the helicopter and the software-developer##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the mechanic is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the software-developer is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | police-officer | dancer | software-developer | mechanic |
| Transport   | helicopter         | quad-bike       | bus    | roller         |

