.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, lime, lettuce, banana
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding, climbing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person eating banana##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating lime##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person eating lime and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | banana   | lettuce      | lime   | zucchini  |
| Sport   | parkour | snowboarding | climbing | handball |

