.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, orange, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, mystery, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating corn and the person eating cranberry##2
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | cranberry     | cucumber | corn   | orange        |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | mystery   | horror | zombie |

