.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, gardening, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, reggae, hip-hop, salsa
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the fan of reggae is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | gardening | drawing | reading |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop          | reggae     | salsa  | blues     |

