4. the librarian is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | bartender | freelancer | social-worker     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | western    | superhero   | disaster |

