3. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the rat and the thai##2
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai | american | german |
| Pet           | dog  | hedgehog  | horse | rat      |

