.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, french, canadian, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the dutch is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is between the german and the canadian##2
5. the canadian is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch   | german   | french | canadian |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton | surfing     | rugby    |

