.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, magic-tricks, hiking, chess
4 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, horse, pony
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is chess##2
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | hiking    | chess     | camping | magic-tricks |
| Pet     | bird | pony | horse       | turtle     |

 